if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('StopReason')
and type = 'U')
drop table StopReason
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: StopReason */
/*==============================================================*/
create table StopReason (
ID int identity(1,1),
ReasonID varchar(50) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS null,
ReasonName varchar(50) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS null
)
go
